WEBVTT

00:00:00.900 --> 00:00:11.860
Speaking practice for botch, impede, quaff, recollect and exacerbate.

00:00:11.970 --> 00:00:13.410
Listen to what I say

00:00:13.650 --> 00:00:16.950
then pause the video and repeat after me.

00:00:17.160 --> 00:00:20.940
Think about the meaning of the vocabulary we studied.

00:00:20.940 --> 00:00:24.630
Train your brain to master these words.

00:00:24.630 --> 00:00:25.930
Let's get started.

00:00:30.270 --> 00:00:36.000
We botched our first attempt at starting a business but we made a success of it

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:37.770
the second time round.

00:00:44.880 --> 00:00:51.410
The people believe that the government is impeding the development of the country and so wish to vote

00:00:51.410 --> 00:00:52.700
in a new one.

00:00:59.030 --> 00:01:04.940
We quaffed the cool water from the stream and relaxed in the warm sunshine.

00:01:12.050 --> 00:01:16.270
Do you recollect anything from the day your house was broken into?

00:01:17.990 --> 00:01:23.680
Yes. I remember there were a few strange people walking up and down the street.

00:01:30.340 --> 00:01:36.240
The company made huge losses this year, and to exacerbate the situation,

00:01:36.370 --> 00:01:39.510
it is under police investigation for fraud.

00:01:47.400 --> 00:01:53.780
Ronaldo has botched his penalty kick and that means Brazil has won the World Cup.

00:02:00.680 --> 00:02:04.390
Even though he was impeded with a severe injury,

00:02:04.640 --> 00:02:09.350
the brave runner completed the marathon after six hours.

00:02:16.240 --> 00:02:19.390
Where's the bottle of red wine I bought yesterday?

00:02:20.770 --> 00:02:24.890
Sorry. Peter and I quaffed it last night with dinner.

00:02:32.690 --> 00:02:37.360
Jane and I met last night for the first time in years.

00:02:37.490 --> 00:02:41.320
We were recollecting all our fun adventures from childhood.

00:02:49.100 --> 00:02:54.590
Don't lift those heavy boxes, otherwise you'll exacerbate your back pain.

00:02:55.290 --> 00:02:56.930
Let me move them for you.